fields.description: This is a strange new breed of auth_check that concerns itself with the update_dict.  It ensures that the update_dict is only attempting to add items from the list of allowed primary keys to the attribute on the actee.  It will return false if any 'remove' operation is in the dict, or if any primary key appears in the add list that is not in the allowed primary key list.
